==市場銷量==
專輯發行首周便於英國本土售出62,650碟，是2009年度首張專輯首週銷售量最佳成績。<ref>{{cite web |last=Sexton |first=Paul |url=http://www.billboard.com/#/news/michael-jackson-maintains-u-k-chart-dominance-1003990605.story |title=Michael Jackson Maintains U.K. Chart Dominance |work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]] |publisher=[[Nielsen_Company|Nielsen Business Media, Inc]] |date=6 July 2009 |accessdate=6 July 2009 |archive-date=2012-09-20 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120920/http://www.billboard.com/%23/news/usher-introduces-teen-singer-justin-bieber-1003966989.story#/news/michael-jackson-maintains-u-k-chart-dominance-1003990605.story |dead-url=no }}</ref>這個記錄最後被[[Florence_and_the_Machine|Florence and the Machine]]樂團的首張專輯''[[Lungs_(album)|Lungs]]''打敗，後者共售出63,020碟。<ref>{{cite web |last=Levine |first=Nick |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a164776/jackson-holds-florence-off-albums-top-spot.html |title=Jackson holds Florence off albums top spot |work=''[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]'' |date=12 July 2009 |accessdate=12 July 2009 |archive-date=2012-07-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6922qq3R6?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a164776/jackson-holds-florence-off-albums-top-spot.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 此專輯在英國本土共計售出350,000碟。<ref>{{cite web |last=Balls |first=David |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/news/a191807/simon-cowell-responds-to-la-roux-criticism.html |title=Simon Cowell responds to La Roux criticism |work=''[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]'' |date=17 December 2009 |accessdate=17 December 2009 |archive-date=2012-07-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6922rkC9f?url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/music/s103/the-x-factor/news/a191807/simon-cowell-responds-to-la-roux-criticism.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

